Not at all.

20:32.940 --> 20:40.360
Hysteresis, in state-space models, describes a system where the path forward is fundamentally different from the path backward.

20:40.820 --> 20:41.120
Right.

20:41.120 --> 20:53.700
So, Flyxion applies a functional to map the asymmetry between the destruction cost, which is the energy required to lose an operator, and the restoration cost, the energy required to reacquire it.

