The observer develops the topological loop that orbits the missing core, but they lack the operators to traverse the interior space.

24:32.260 --> 24:39.000
This maps flawlessly onto the clinical observation of confabulatory behavior in patients with severe neural trauma.

24:39.300 --> 24:39.620
It does.

