And neurological models have historically struggled to explain the precise mechanism of that generative fabrication.

25:09.020 --> 25:12.660
Why do they invent Flyxion's geometry provides the answer.

25:12.860 --> 25:17.740
The confabulation is the topological signature of a vector field flowing around a singularity.

25:17.740 --> 25:18.220
Exactly.

