The brain is attempting to maintain a continuous logical path through the manifold, but it is forced to navigate around a non-contractable one-dimensional hole.

25:27.560 --> 25:28.680
It is circling the void.

25:29.120 --> 25:33.480
The system is navigating around invisible topological constraints it can no longer see.

25:33.480 --> 25:40.180
So the complexity of the false narrative is directly proportional to the size of the topological hole it is trying to bypass.

