The replication crisis in the psychological and biomedical sciences is traditionally attributed to malicious pastman care, statistical anomalies, or outright fraud.

28:25.760 --> 28:30.680
We assume the original researchers lied, or the current researchers are just incompetent.

28:30.820 --> 28:34.380
But Flyxion models it as a failure of the admissibility boundary.

28:34.720 --> 28:36.220
A collective repair failure.

28:36.280 --> 28:36.600
Exactly.

