The original result was dependent on highly specific, tacit, experimental operators, like the unique calibration of analog equipment, the localized environmental conditions of that specific lab, the undocumented physical techniques of the graduate students running the assays.

29:14.580 --> 29:17.300
Over 20 years, those graduate students retire.

29:18.120 --> 29:22.660
The analog equipment is replaced by digital sensors with completely different noise floors.

29:23.320 --> 29:25.080
The tacit operators are lost.

29:25.080 --> 29:29.000
And the admissibility boundary of the scientific community silently contracts.

29:29.620 --> 29:33.140
When modern researchers attempt to replicate the finding, they fail.

29:33.520 --> 29:37.420
Not necessarily because the 1998 finding was fraudulent.

