29:44.600 --> 29:50.620
Results that scientists thought were safely inside the restorable interior of knowledge were actually outside the boundary.

29:50.880 --> 29:52.480
The boundary was mislocated.

29:52.480 --> 29:54.980
The collective repair repertoire degraded.

29:54.980 --> 30:01.740
And the hysteresis cost of perfectly recreating the 1998 experimental conditions just reached infinity.

