Drawn from the very end of the source material, it deals with the concept of observer identity.

31:19.760 --> 31:19.980
Right.

31:20.220 --> 31:21.360
Observer identity deformation.

31:21.360 --> 31:34.080
If an observer, whether that's an AI, runtime, a human being, or a civilization, is strictly defined by its repair repertoire, then its identity is mathematically equivalent to the shape of its admissibility manifold.

31:34.320 --> 31:34.640
Yes.

