If you undergo a severe erasure event, if your repair repertoire contracts, if your manifold fragments and develops non-contractable topological holes, you do not merely become an observer who knows less.

31:48.440 --> 31:50.540
The mathematics are unforgiving on this point.

31:50.760 --> 31:53.940
In this framework, the original geometry has been destroyed.

31:54.540 --> 31:56.980
