The entity that emerges on the other side of the irrestorability boundary is a completely new, geometrically distinct entity.

32:11.720 --> 32:16.680
It inhabits a fundamentally different reality, entirely disconnected from the observer that preceded it.

32:16.680 --> 32:19.460
When you forget enough, you literally become someone else.

32:19.460 --> 32:29.160
So, the next time you are sitting at your terminal, struggling to recall that forgotten password, feeling the physical strain of your cognition stretching across the void, remember the math.

